{"tid":2373512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"用開咩中文輸入法？","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:27:33.000Z","uid":390261,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"99ab260c6cafc39e556dd373005072ebee02ea38","tid":2373512,"uid":390261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"中文字本身就難打 小弟中五之前一直用緊速成<br />\n後嚟中文老師俾咗份報告我哋做 小弟打個一千字打咗差吾多成晚<br />\n事後超級後悔 所以下定決心學倉頡<br />\n打開倉頡之後覺得倉頡好王道 有少少睇吾起其他打字法<br />\n倉頡重碼率低 拆字符合漢字結構 可以實現盲打 如果跟住份稿打嘅話吾會有打吾到生僻字嘅問題<br />\n相反語音好容易吾識讀個字就吾識打<br />\n不過彷間一直都指倉頡難學 所以而家識打倉頡嘅人好似好少<br />\n吾知而家啲人用開咩輸入法？"},{"pid":"abc4c48a94307ce07fe3e672eefa77b6b3a00fac","tid":2373512,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"咪又係吾吾吾 死弱智仔跳樓死啦"},{"pid":"14070eadadb7d34e6019c4ccefd2f50ad0ef0bf5","tid":2373512,"uid":126649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"唔=口一一口"},{"pid":"ae82d4000d0f836ac202250f64bf8b480e85ac78","tid":2373512,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"你依啲 5p 狗唔好影衰倉頡撚嘅 reputation"},{"pid":"14da461b73323f86544c656fd463b9d347629dab","tid":2373512,"uid":78856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔起其他打字法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學好中文先學打字啦傻閪"},{"pid":"5d851b13dad0855d7b9b78e6956974fb1fa00dc4","tid":2373512,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"倉頡最快 不服來電"},{"pid":"cec62c7c5df9bec8effcc61f1cf5a442cadfb1fd","tid":2373512,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"學咩輸入法，你學好中文字先啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3657a16781c344c3b435784b7633d0938128d03d","tid":2373512,"uid":387452,"like":0,"dis